<p>
    We chose Debian because of its reliability, security, simple installation 
    and a huge stock of free high quality software. In our datacenter, we have 
    26 servers running Debian (stable version) and five workstations (datacenter 
    administrators staff). These last with KDE and GNOME.
</p>

<p>
    On our servers we have: apache2, mysql, cups, NFS, FTP, postgres, postfix,
    spamassasin, clamav, courier mail server, squid, squidguard, shorewall,
    LDAP, bind9, isc-dhcp-server, openvpn, openssl, joomla, samba, nagios,
    moodle, Xen for virtualization, etc.
</p>
